 semiboil the pasta,
 seive the semi boil pasta,
 take a frying pan and heat it,
 then put some butter in it ,
 and add all the vegetables in it,
 tosse the vegetables for 3 minutes,
 then add pasta in it and mix them well,
 add some salt, black pepper ,
 1/2 cup of milk 
 little bit water and 1cup cheese
 mix them well and cover with the lid,
 stem it for 2-3 minutes ,
 open the lid add pasta sauce,herbs;
 mix them well

 then serve it hot 
 example for serving 
 you can serve it with the garlic bread
 and also
 granish it with normal cheese and herbs


 